name: The Printer is Out
description:
Your Printer has a weird error! To fix it you have to gather lots of... bugs, ribbons, mushrooms and...trash?

A slightly surreal game done for Quarantine Jam and Extra Credits Fan Jam#2.

Not well balanced right now.

You can complete it in less than 5 minutes.

Themes: 

Out of Print, A Lot Of: The Printer is 'Out of Print', and you need 'A Lot Of' the weird components to fix it.

To play, just click on things.
